{"title":"Wolf Tooth WT-1 Synthetic Chain Lube cleans, lubes, & protects in one blue/green bottle","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/06/08/wolf-tooth-wt-1-synthetic-chain-lube-cleans-lubes-protects-in-one-blue-green-bottle/","date":1623168017000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-3\"></span><em>Another&nbsp;</em>chain lube? Yeah, that was my first reaction, too. There has been no shortage of <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/?s=chain+lube\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">new lubes</a> lately, with everything from <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/10/14/pumpkin-spice-chain-lube-special-batch-of-bike-hardcore-chain-butter-teases-new-scent/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Pumpkin Spice</a> to <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/04/25/silca-super-secret-chain-lube-liquifies-drag-with-bottled-hot-melt-wax/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Super Secret</a> formulas. But instead of another take on wax, Wolf Tooth Components has finally released their WT-1 All Conditions Chain Lube – and it’s worth checking out.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222906/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-2.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222906/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-2.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb13/ng:webp/ngcb13\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth WT-1 Synthetic Chain Lube blot\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222906/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-2.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb13 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222906/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-2-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb13 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222906/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-2-800x533.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb13 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222906/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-2-120x80.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb13 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222906/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-2-768x512.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb13 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222906/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-2-696x464.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb13 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222906/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-2-1068x712.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb13 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222906/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-2-630x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb13 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222906/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-2.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb13/ng:webp/ngcb13\" ezoid=\"0.5051052765625965\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222906/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-2.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb13 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222906/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-2-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb13 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222906/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-2-800x533.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb13 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222906/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-2-120x80.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb13 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222906/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-2-768x512.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb13 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222906/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-2-696x464.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb13 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222906/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-2-1068x712.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb13 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222906/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-2-630x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb13 630w\"></a></p><p>Is it blue? Is it green? Whatever you want to call it, WT-1 is quite colorful which helps you see where it’s been applied.</p><p>Calling it an All Conditions Synthetic Chain Lube, WT-1 boasts properties of dry lube, wet lube, chain cleaner, and a drivetrain treatment all in one. Sounds too good to be true. But then again, that’s what led Wolf Tooth Components to partner with SCC Tech to bring WT-1 to market.<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-medrectangle-3\"></span></p><p>When asked how WT-1 compares to <a href=\"https://www.scctech.bike/products/2oz-scc-slick-the-all-conditions-lubricant-solution\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">SCC Tech’s own Drivetrain Treatment</a>, Wolf Tooth’s Brendan Moore told us that, “both chain lubricants rely on the same formulation. If you’ve liked using SCC Slick, you can expect the same great performance from WT-1 Chain Lube.”</p><p><span><iframe width=\"696\" height=\"392\" data-ezsrc=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/-Gz2suXxDbk?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\"></iframe></span></p><p>What does that mean? If means that you should end up with a very clean chain lube that lasts a claimed 3-5x longer than the competition. WTC calls out the fact that WT-1 is 95% chain lube and 5% carrier fluid. Other chain lubes can be as low as 20-50% lubricant. But even with most of the fluid being actual lubricant, the WT-1 fluid is still a low enough viscosity to easily flow into the the rollers and fully coat the chain.</p><p>Additionally, a “detergent-like additive” is included to clean your chain as it lubricates. That forces all those contaminants to the surface where they can be wiped away. The lubricant is said to then bond to the metal plates of the chain to protect all surfaces, decreasing wear.</p><p><strong>WT-1 Claims:</strong></p><ul><li>Cleans, lubricates, and protects chains</li><li>Peak performance in all conditions</li><li>Optimal choice for complex&nbsp;modern drivetrains</li><li>Available in 2.0 and 0.5 fl oz bottles, sold individually and by the box</li><li>Easy to use; application takes about 10 minutes</li><li>Also works on other places of your bike, including hubs, cables, and&nbsp;pulley wheels</li></ul><h2>First Impressions</h2><figure id=\"attachment_261301\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-261301\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222911/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-3.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222911/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-3.jpg\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth WT-1 Synthetic Chain Lube on chain\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222911/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-3.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222911/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-3-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222911/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-3-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222911/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-3-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222911/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-3-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222911/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-3-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222911/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-3-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222911/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-3-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222911/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-3.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222911/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-3.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222911/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-3-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222911/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-3-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222911/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-3-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222911/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-3-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222911/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-3-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222911/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-3-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222911/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-3-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-261301\">Don’t be alarmed. Your chain won’t be Smurfed forever.</figcaption></figure><p>From the very first application, three things stood out about WT-1. It goes on very bluish-green, it flows easily through the chain, and the self-cleaning claims seem to be true.<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-medrectangle-4\"></span></p><p>I started by adding a drop of WT-1 to each roller of a very well-used SRAM Eagle 12 speed chain. Initially it shows up as bright blue, making you think it’s going to make a mess of everything it touches. But that blue quickly fades as it works its way into the chain after a few pedal rotations.</p><figure id=\"attachment_261303\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-261303\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222921/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-5.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222921/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-5.jpg\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth WT-1 Synthetic Chain Lube clean chain after application\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222921/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-5.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222921/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-5-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222921/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-5-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222921/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-5-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222921/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-5-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222921/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-5-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222921/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-5-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222921/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-5-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222921/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-5.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222921/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-5.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222921/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-5-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222921/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-5-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222921/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-5-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222921/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-5-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222921/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-5-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222921/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-5-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222921/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula-5-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-261303\">Before even leaving the stand, after a couple of wipes, this super dirty chain was already starting to look clean from a WT-1 application.</figcaption></figure><p>Soon, you’ll start to see all the gunk hidden inside your chain work its way to the surface where it can be wiped away. I was surprised to even see tiny bits of metal on the rag after the first application.</p><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-4\"></span>It will continue to clean the chain for the first few rides, and WTC recommends wiping off the chain at the end of the ride, but not adding more chain lube until it really needs it.</p><h2><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-large-leaderboard-2\"></span>Application</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07223633/Wolf-Tooth-Comonents-WT-1-chain-lub-all-conditions-with-applicator-tip-3.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07223633/Wolf-Tooth-Comonents-WT-1-chain-lub-all-conditions-with-applicator-tip-3.jpg\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth WT-1 Synthetic Chain Lube application\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07223633/Wolf-Tooth-Comonents-WT-1-chain-lub-all-conditions-with-applicator-tip-3.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07223633/Wolf-Tooth-Comonents-WT-1-chain-lub-all-conditions-with-applicator-tip-3-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07223633/Wolf-Tooth-Comonents-WT-1-chain-lub-all-conditions-with-applicator-tip-3-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07223633/Wolf-Tooth-Comonents-WT-1-chain-lub-all-conditions-with-applicator-tip-3-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07223633/Wolf-Tooth-Comonents-WT-1-chain-lub-all-conditions-with-applicator-tip-3-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07223633/Wolf-Tooth-Comonents-WT-1-chain-lub-all-conditions-with-applicator-tip-3-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07223633/Wolf-Tooth-Comonents-WT-1-chain-lub-all-conditions-with-applicator-tip-3-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07223633/Wolf-Tooth-Comonents-WT-1-chain-lub-all-conditions-with-applicator-tip-3-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07223633/Wolf-Tooth-Comonents-WT-1-chain-lub-all-conditions-with-applicator-tip-3.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07223633/Wolf-Tooth-Comonents-WT-1-chain-lub-all-conditions-with-applicator-tip-3.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07223633/Wolf-Tooth-Comonents-WT-1-chain-lub-all-conditions-with-applicator-tip-3-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07223633/Wolf-Tooth-Comonents-WT-1-chain-lub-all-conditions-with-applicator-tip-3-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07223633/Wolf-Tooth-Comonents-WT-1-chain-lub-all-conditions-with-applicator-tip-3-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07223633/Wolf-Tooth-Comonents-WT-1-chain-lub-all-conditions-with-applicator-tip-3-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07223633/Wolf-Tooth-Comonents-WT-1-chain-lub-all-conditions-with-applicator-tip-3-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07223633/Wolf-Tooth-Comonents-WT-1-chain-lub-all-conditions-with-applicator-tip-3-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07223633/Wolf-Tooth-Comonents-WT-1-chain-lub-all-conditions-with-applicator-tip-3-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>One of the biggest selling points of WT-1 seems to be the ease of application. There’s no need to clean the chain up front, and you don’t have to be super careful in how much lube is applied to the chain. The process should only take about 10 minutes, and most of that is waiting before the final wipe down.</p><p><strong>WTC Application directions:</strong></p><ol><li>Shake bottle of WT-1 for 30 seconds. A ball bearing is present in every bottle to help mix things up.</li><li>Apply one drop to each roller of your chain. We recommend applying WT-1 Chain Lube to the top side of your chain between your derailleur and chainring, just in front of that lower&nbsp;pulley wheel.</li><li>Backpedal 20-30 times. This helps WT-1 Chain Lube find its way between all the pieces of your chain.</li><li>Wait 5-10 minutes. Pretty simple.</li><li>Wipe chain with microfiber cloth until it appears clean with a light sheen. It’ll look extra dirty at first, then it will clear up as you wipe away that dirt.</li><li>Ride your bike. Reapply at least once every 400 miles.</li></ol><h2>Pricing and Availability:</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222927/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07222927/Wolf-Tooth-Components-WT-1-chainlube-all-conditions-formula.jpg\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth WT-1 Synthetic Chain Lube bottles\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/